quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  41,25,"Nefka yasen imeddukwal i sen icebbĂȘen ayen illan zdat sen, akked wayen illan deffir sen. IĂ»aĂŽ fellasen wawal ger leoyus n yimdanen akw n leonun, i i$aben, uqbel nnsen. Ih, nitni d imexsuĂŽen"
  41,26,"Nnan wid ijehlen: \"ur ssemĂȘaset i LeqwĂŽan agi. Ssekret fellas, ta$wegwa, ahat a prebĂȘem"
