  41,28,"D wagi ay d aqeĂźĂźi icenga n Ăebbi: times; i nitni degs axxam n lebda; d aqeĂźĂźi, imi la nekĂŽen issekniyen nneÂŁ"
  41,29,"Ad inin, wid ijehlen: \"a Mass nne$! Essken a$ wid i $ i$elĂźen, d loenn ne$ d amdan; a ten neĂŽkev, ad u$alen seg wid indellen mavi"
  41,30,"Ih, wid innan: \"Mass nne$ d Ăebbi\", sinna, nudan lewqama, a d rsent $uĂŽsen lmalayek: \"ur ppagwadet, ur $webblet; ppubeccĂŽet s Loennet i wen ippuwaĂąĂąden"
  41,31,"Nekwni d imawlan nnwen di tmeddurt n ddunit u di laxeĂŽt. Dinna, i kunwi, ayen i cedhant teĂŽwiĂȘin nnwen. Dinna, i kunwi, ayen tessutrem"
  41,32,"D tarusi s$uĂŽ Win IpsemmiĂȘen, IpĂȘunun"
  41,33,"Anwa yifen awal umĂąin n win inaĂąĂŽen Ăebbi, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, id innan: \"nek, ih, seg imvuĂąen"
  41,34,"Ur iaĂądil ise$ akked tucmip. Err ip akin, s wayen ip yifen. Ma tella cceĂȘna, garak d yiwen, ad iu$al d aĂȘbib i k iĂȘemmlen"
  41,35,"Ur teppunefk siwa i wid iĂ»ebbĂŽen. Ur teppunefk, siwa i bu sser abarar"
  41,36,"Ma iccacev ak CciĂźan tuccva, ssuter laĂąnaya n Ăebbi. Ih, Neppa d win Isellen, d Amusnaw"
  41,37,"Seg issekniyen iS, ass akked yiv, iĂźij akked waggur. Ur kennut ara i yiĂźij, ne$ i waggur. Knut i Ăebbi, iten id Ixelqen, ma d Neppa ay tĂąabbdem"
  41,38,"Ma zuxxen, ihi, wid illan ar Mass ik, sbuccuĂąen T iv akked wass, ur Ăąaggun"
  41,39,"Seg issekniyen iS: a pwaliv, keĂ§Ă§, akal iqquĂŽ; lemmer ad as Nesse$li aman, a d iakwi, ad icuff. Win it id Issadren, d Win ara d Issidren lmeggtin. Ih, Neppa, Izmer i yal cci"
  41,40,"Ih, wid issexĂ»aĂŽen issekniyen nneÂŁ, ur drigen fellaneÂŁ. Menyif win ara ipwaveggĂŽen ar tmes, ne$ win ara iasen di laman, ass n tnekra? Xedmet ayen i wen ihwan. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali ayen txeddmem"
  41,41,"Akka, wid inekĂŽen asmekti, mi ten id iusa, u neppat ard Tazmamt tuzmirt"
  41,42,"Ur d iusi le$wlav zdat es, ne$ deffir es. D tarusi s$uĂŽ Bab n Ă»Ă»wab, AmaĂązuz"
  41,43,"Awal i k id iusan, d win kan id iusan imazanen, uqbel ik. Mass ik, ih, ard Bab n ssmaĂȘ, d Bab uĂąaqeb aqeĂŽĂȘan"
  41,44,"Lemmer Nerri LeqwĂŽan s tmeslayt tabeĂŽĂŽanit, a d inin: \"lemmer feĂ»Ă»len issekniyen iS s wawal abeĂŽĂŽani, u s taĂąĂŽabt\"? Ini: \"neppa, i wid iumnen, d nnhaya u d ccafuĂąa. Wid ur numin ara, ĂąaĂ©gent tmejjin nnsen. Neppa, i nitni, d tider$elt. Widak pwanecden seg umkan ibaĂąden"
  41,45,"Ni$ Nefka yas Tazmamt i Musa. Mgarraden fellas. Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal s$uĂŽ Mass ik, yili tefra garasen. Nitni, fellas, di ccekk imcebbwel"
  41,46,"Win ixedmen ayen ilhan, i iman is; win iccven, mgal iman is. Mass ik ur Idennis ara imdanen"